4 MAX. NO. OF EMPLOYEES 1,538
5
6 SECTION 2. EXTRA HELP. There is hereby authorized, for the Department
7 of Corrections - Division of Community Correction for the 2025-2026 fiscal
8 year, the following maximum number of part-time or temporary employees, to be
9 known as "Extra Help", payable from funds appropriated herein for such
10 purposes: ten (10) temporary or part-time employees, when needed, at rates of
11 pay not to exceed those provided in the Uniform Classification and
12 Compensation Act, or its successor, or this act for the appropriate
13 classification.
14
15 SECTION 3. APPROPRIATION - STATE OPERATIONS. There is hereby
16 appropriated, to the Department of Corrections, to be payable from the
17 Division of Community Correction Fund Account, for personal services and
18 operating expenses of the Department of Corrections - Division of Community
19 Correction - State Operations for the fiscal year ending June 30, 2026, the
20 following:
21
22 ITEM FISCAL YEAR
23 NO. 2025-2026
24 (01) REGULAR SALARIES $74,004,853
25 (02) EXTRA HELP 100,000
26 (03) PERSONAL SERVICES MATCHING 29,688,116
27 (04) OVERTIME 210,000
28 (05) MAINT. & GEN. OPERATION
29 (A) OPER. EXPENSE 13,710,795
30 (B) CONF. & TRAVEL 32,880
31 (C) PROF. FEES 168,729
32 (D) CAP. OUTLAY 0
33 (E) DATA PROC. 0
34 (06) REENTRY 5,285,000
35 TOTAL AMOUNT APPROPRIATED $123,200,373
36
